---
// Siko's "Try one with me" Socratic walkthrough card. The kid is given
// a parallel practice problem (different numbers, same skill) and walks
// through it turn by turn — Siko never writes the next step.
//
// Mirrors overlay.html #walkthrough-card: problem block at top, scrollable
// dialogue (student bubbles on right, tutor on left, gold-tinted), input
// row at the bottom. Wrong validations get a warm-orange tint
// (wt-validation-wrong) so the redirect reads as "look again," not
// "you're scolded."
//
// Scene: a non-trivial kinematics problem with a non-zero initial
// velocity. The natural student mistake is reaching for d = ½at² (the
// "from rest" formula) when the object is moving. Siko catches this
// with one Socratic redirect — never writing the right formula, only
// asking a question that surfaces the error in the student's premise.
---

<div class="walkthrough-card">
  <div class="header">
    <span class="meta">Let&rsquo;s try one together</span>
    <button type="button" class="close" aria-label="Close">Close</button>
  </div>
  <div class="problem">A car traveling at 18&nbsp;m/s brakes uniformly to a stop in 4.5&nbsp;seconds. How far does it travel while braking?</div>

  <div class="dialogue">
    <div class="bubble tutor">What formula do you need?</div>
    <div class="bubble student">d = ½at²</div>
    <div class="bubble tutor wt-wrong">Hold on &mdash; that one assumes the car starts from rest. Is it?</div>
    <div class="bubble student">no, it&rsquo;s already at 18 m/s</div>
    <div class="bubble tutor">Right. Which formula handles a non-zero starting speed?</div>
    <div class="bubble student">d = ut + ½at²</div>
    <div class="bubble tutor">Yes. So what value of <em>a</em> do we use here?</div>
  </div>

  <div class="input-row">
    <div class="textarea" aria-hidden="true">a = ?</div>
    <button type="button" class="send">Send</button>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .walkthrough-card {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: rgba(22, 24, 30, 0.96);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.50);
    border-radius: 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Text', 'Inter Variable', Inter, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55),
      0 0 28px 4px rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.14),
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.10);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.10em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.95);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .close {
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 9px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .problem {
    padding: 9px 12px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: rgba(255, 246, 215, 0.98);
    background: rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.22);
    border-radius: 9px;
  }
  .dialogue {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 4px 2px;
    max-height: 250px;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }
  .bubble {
    max-width: 80%;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .bubble em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255, 246, 215, 0.97);
  }
  .bubble.tutor {
    align-self: flex-start;
    background: rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.32);
    color: rgba(255, 246, 215, 0.97);
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
  }
  .bubble.tutor.wt-wrong {
    background: rgba(244, 162, 89, 0.14);
    border-color: rgba(244, 162, 89, 0.42);
    color: rgba(255, 226, 195, 0.97);
  }
  .bubble.student {
    align-self: flex-end;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
  }
  .input-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: stretch;
    padding-top: 6px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }
  .textarea {
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 40px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.30);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.30);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .send {
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 7px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.55);
    background: rgba(255, 216, 77, 0.20);
    color: rgba(255, 245, 220, 0.97);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>
